                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5271" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0477</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8488 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">谁主沉浮：王小羽家族式创业折戟 </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Who is in charge of ups and downs: the failure of Wang Xiaoyu&#39;s family entrepreneurship</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">傅颖，何筠，窦军生</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南昌大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东海县恒利面粉厂</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家族企业；创业；农业；企业破产；人力资本；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">family business; entrepreneurship; agriculture; business bankruptcy; human resource</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了一个紧随中国经济发展，具有典型代表性的中国家族企业创业和公司创业的故事，阐述了其从无到有，从小到大最终不幸破产的故事。1995年在国有面粉厂做工的王小羽作为家族核心创始人辞职与妻子一起成立了村办企业——团林面粉厂，后续王小羽招募了11位家族成员进厂工作，面粉厂取得了快速成长。2010年王小羽进行公司创业，公司也更名为白龙马面业，家族成员基本处于中高管的位置，隔年王小羽上马生产线二期，但却最终因为资金紧张而走向破产。家族企业创业初期，企业规模小，其核心成员基本上是以血缘、亲缘为纽带的家族成员，创业者作为核心拥有天然的家长权威，依靠家长权威的家族式管理即可保证家族企业顺利运转。但当家族企业试图扩大规模进行公司创业时，家族制的弊端可能凸显。本案例重点围绕家族性资源在家族企业创业过程和后续公司创业中的作用展开讨论，旨在启发学员对家族企业创业与发展的思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The case describes a typical family business following the development of China&#39;s economy. This is also a failure case of entrepreneurship, which represents the story of its founding, from small to large, and finally unfortunately bankruptcy. In 1995, Wang Xiaoyu, who worked in the state-owned flour factory, resigned and set up a village-owned enterprise - TuanLin flour factory with his wife. In 2002, the village-owned enterprise was restructured and the Donghai HengLi flour factory was established. After the restructuring, Wang Xiaoyu recruited ten family members to work in the factory. In 2010, Wang Xiaoyu set up the BaiLongMa noodle business, and the family members were basically in the position of middle and senior managers. Wang Xiaoyu, who owned 100% of BaiLongMa in 2011, went on the second phase of the production line, but eventually went bankrupt due to the lack of funds. After the bankruptcy, Wang Xiaoyu&#39;s family is still United, and there is a voice to let Wang Xiaoyu return to the enterprise&#39;s management. In the early stage of a family business, the enterprise&#39;s scale is small, and its core members are family members with blood relationship. As the core, owner-manager has natural paternalistic authority, and relying on family management can ensure firms&#39; smooth operation. But when the family business tries to make further development by corporate entrepreneurship, the disadvantages of the family system will also be highlighted. This case focuses on the role of family resources in the process of the nascent entrepreneurship and corporate entrepreneurship, aiming to inspire the students to think about the entrepreneurship and development of family firms.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家族企业创业 公司创业</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
